Title: 'The power of &quot;saudade&quot; '
DateModified: '2019-03-07'
DatePublished: '2019-03-07'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/the-power-of-saudade
SetInCountry: Portugal
Category: Making a local connection
AuthorName: Leonardo  Henriques
AuthorCountry: Brazil
Text: If in your language you don't have one word that can express the deeply meaning
  of missing something, someone or anything, you must understand what "saudade" means
  in Portuguese. And this is my goal in Portugal. Investigate, ask locals, artists,
  teachers, sociologists, scientists what the meaning of "saudade"!
